Frank--I have listened to this APSR broadcast and was incredibly impressed with what occurred at this event. Chris&#39;s box is quite capable of behaving like John Edward--directly bringing relations through to talk to those who need to hear them. Some of the responses were astoundingly clear and loud. It certainly sounded similar to what I have heard of what Bruce is getting, and honestly, it is exactly what I hope to get with my box when I receive it.

If you haven&#39;t listened to this, you really should. I think Chris made his usual statements about Edison and the 30, but aside from that, this was a wonderful session and people were extremely moved.

If you want, I&#39;ll find the URL.

Ann



